都仲未搵到 無人敢出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n行出黎既代價實在太大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 出得黎又要夠能力，真係難搵"},{"pid":"6f8b0b0bafd82651cfbc21eea8d1c2181f856fd9","tid":26143,"uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T15:14:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>希望快啲有人出黎接到天琦班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 : 支持本民前</blockquote><br />\n2018年1月 就開審<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n聽左channel i一段時間<br />\n天琦比人禁選個陣已經講緊希望可以搵到人接班<br />\n佢同ray就退居幕後讀書等開審<br />\n但都而家都仲未搵到 無人敢出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n行出黎既代價實在太大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 出得黎又要夠能力，真係難搵</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果到開審前都無人肯出黎<br />\n本民前應該要滅黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc6a6102609256810cbe271a43bc9cd2d6bf10ab","tid":26143,"uid":38572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T15:18:14.000Z","msg":"無人敢出嚟喇, 有都俾人屌到仆街, 仲要係屌得最多係同路人"},{"pid":"e71137f0cc8b416236f7cd5f46002ff1bb6d3c78","tid":26143,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T15:41:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無人敢出嚟喇, 有都俾人屌到仆街, 仲要係屌得最多係同路人</blockquote><br />\n一係人講乜信乜果班真心膠,其餘果班根本唔係同路人"},{"pid":"6d5b1bae07d07e92b297c809947404407e5d4d75","tid":26143,"uid":24013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T02:31:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>無人敢出嚟喇, 有都俾人屌到仆街, 仲要係屌得最多係同路人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一係人講乜信乜果班真心膠,其餘果班根本唔係同路人</blockquote><br />\n熱狗只係不斷攻擊最接近自己既人，一開始攻擊民主黨，然後社民連再到人力，然後青政本民前，就係所謂既屌票。"},{"pid":"e22fa3e81f8a769f6ca375bc1e94d772b46a604a","tid":26143,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T02:33:28.000Z","msg":"Me <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44a89dffaf940d09ab64b25e5ced42bb107defde","tid":26143,"uid":3560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T02:36:00.000Z","msg":"屌支那就支持"},{"pid":"18e029efa92067add9d76f096e4482230334b78d","tid":26143,"uid":24013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T03:32:08.000Z","msg":"以而家既形勢，本土必須團結，但好可惜熱狗只係私怨撚"},{"pid":"2deb78c7c1ce9e87c58360cb4503834e4204e679","tid":26143,"uid":5750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T03:58:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9f2a3e3123c179bb10078c534132f81357bc31a4","tid":26143,"uid":5750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T03:59:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6063ec1a4c87adaa9d08858121c5593be5451192","tid":26143,"uid":24013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T03:59:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>以而家既形勢，本土必須團結，但好可惜熱狗只係私怨撚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實大家都係私怨撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可唔可以唔好再自己人打自己人</blockquote><br />\n我都希望，但你睇下熱狗黃洋達同埋垃圾四眼日日fb　講乜鳩，<br />\n利申：港島投垃圾四眼"},{"pid":"3f69543e55e16ec85fe7aa37c9b234b54aec2e10","tid":26143,"uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T04:59:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>以而家既形勢，本土必須團結，但好可惜熱狗只係私怨撚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實大家都係私怨撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可唔可以唔好再自己人打自己人</blockquote><br />\n我都希望，但你睇下熱狗黃洋達同埋垃圾四眼日日fb　講乜鳩，<br />\n利申：港島投垃圾四眼</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係 大家都唔想私怨<br />\n至少我無見本民前兩子甚至梁游佢地係有名正言順咁向熱狗開拖<br />\n但熱狗個邊啲大粒就日日開佢地拖<br />\n可以點解決？"},{"pid":"16f0652c81a82d7688b0d2049668d91408649df2","tid":26143,"uid":5149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T05:12:34.000Z","msg":"梁天琦我都算<br />\n本民前 不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/nor